  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc2\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc7 \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Meeting between the Ambassador of Japan and the Minister of Fisheries",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "A meeting between Japanese Ambassador to Sri Lanka Misukoshi Hideki and Fisheries Minister Douglas Devananda, who is on a three day visit to the North, was held in Jaffna yesterday (30).",
        "Minister Douglas Devananda briefed the Japanese envoy on the current political situation, the activities of the Ministry of Fisheries, and especially on the progress made in the production of export quality seafood in aquaculture, including seafood production."
      ],
